<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c2">( ... - ٨٧٠ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">( ... - ١٤٦٦ م)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
